snippet.title: Em8ER First Playable Achieved!
snippet.description:
We did it! Thanks to your support, we now have the first playable buid of Em8ER. This build features the new tropical biome, as well as running, jumping, jetpacking and gliding. This build is available now to all eligible backers at my.em8er.com

TWITCH CHANNEL FOR EXTENDED PLAY: https://www.twitch.tv/grummz_em8er

Animated logo by community member Kaityn! Thank you!
